name: Cupid’s Temptation
description:
‘Cupid’s Temptation' is an video - collage interpretation of a mythical character, combining my expressionist modes of expression and my organic lines.
Roman god of love and sex. In Greek mythology, as  Eros, he is described as one of the children of Aphrodite and Ares.
 Eros was depicted as often carrying a lyre or bow and arrow.
